    "Hybrid feature extraction has been mentioned in studies such as Chen et al.",
    "(2023 In Regan et al. (2022), an autoencoder with the Fisher Feature Extraction method was pivotal in isolating features that are most discriminative between classes of normal behavior and Gafgyt attacks in energy usage datasets.",
